\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.3}{\ignorespaces Ingestion success rate over multiple runs per model for the V2~$\rightarrow $~canonical scenario. Success indicates that the generated transform executed without error and produced a row count matching the baseline. The figure illustrates the variability of \texttt  {llama3} and the more consistent success of the larger hosted model across runs.}}{42}{figure.caption.14}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:canonical-ingestion-success-runs}{{5.3}{42}{Ingestion success rate over multiple runs per model for the V2~$\rightarrow $~canonical scenario. Success indicates that the generated transform executed without error and produced a row count matching the baseline. The figure illustrates the variability of \texttt {llama3} and the more consistent success of the larger hosted model across runs}{figure.caption.14}{}}
